## 4.4 CRUD Operation Mapping Diagram (Mermaid State Diagram)

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Empty: Initial State
    Empty --> Created: POST /students<br/>201 Created
    Created --> Read: GET /students/:id<br/>200 OK
    Created --> Updated: PUT /students/:id<br/>200 OK
    Created --> Deleted: DELETE /students/:id<br/>200 OK
    Read --> Read: GET /students/:id<br/>(Idempotent)
    Updated --> Updated: PUT /students/:id<br/>(Idempotent)
    Deleted --> [*]: Resource Removed
    Created --> NotFound: GET /students/999<br/>404 Not Found
    NotFound --> Created: POST /students<br/>201 Created

    note right of Created: Resource exists in store
    note right of Deleted: Resource purged from store
```
