**(a)** Explain the concept of middleware in Express.js. Discuss the different types of middleware (application-level, router-level, error-handling, built-in, and third-party) with examples. `[7 Marks]`

**(b)** Write an Express.js program that demonstrates the use of multiple middleware functions, route parameters, query strings, and proper error handling for a `/users` API. `[7 Marks]`

