> **KTU Examiner's Valuation Warning / Pitfall Callout:**
> - **Do NOT confuse Mongoose (ODM for NoSQL) with Sequelize/Prisma (ORM for SQL).** Examiners deduct 1–2 marks for this.
> - **Do NOT write `find()` in uppercase or as `FIND()`.** Mongoose is case-sensitive and method-style.
