# SECTION 3 — Step-by-Step Implementation & Analytical Matrix

> [!NOTE]
> The following implementation builds a complete 4×4 Memory Game in pure vanilla JavaScript — no libraries. This is the **exact style** KTU expects in lab records and exam answers.

## 3.1 Step 1 — HTML Skeleton

The HTML defines an 8×8 board structure (which we will render as 4×4). Each card is a `<div>` containing a front face and a back face.

```html
