## 2.2 The TMDB API — Endpoints Used

The **The Movie Database (TMDB)** API is a free, RESTful, JSON-based service. The Movie App typically consumes these endpoints:

| HTTP Method | Endpoint | Purpose | Auth Header |
|:-----------:|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/movie/popular` | Fetch currently popular movies | `Bearer <API_KEY_V4>` |
| `GET` | `/movie/top_rated` | Fetch top-rated movies | `Bearer <API_KEY_V4>` |
