## 2.4 Why This Architecture? — Engineering Justification

- **Component Reusability:** `MovieCard` is reused across Popular, Top Rated, Upcoming, and Search results — promoting the **DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself)** principle.
- **Separation of Concerns:** API logic is isolated in a service layer (`api.js`), making the app maintainable and testable.
- **Single Source of Truth:** Global state (favorites) lives in Context, eliminating inconsistent state across pages.
- **Performance:** Lazy loading images and using `React.memo` on `MovieCard` minimizes re-renders.

