## 2.1 The Three-Tier Architecture (Mandatory Diagram Concept)

Every KTU project evaluation begins with the student drawing or describing this **layered architecture**:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  PRESENTATION TIER  (React, HTML, CSS, JS)      │
│  - User Interface                                │
│  - Client-side validation                        │
│  - State management (Redux/Context API)          │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                     │  HTTP/HTTPS (JSON payloads)
                     ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  APPLICATION TIER  (Node.js, Express.js)        │
│  - Business logic                                │
│  - REST API endpoints                            │
│  - Authentication (JWT)                          │
│  - Input validation                              │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                     │  Mongoose ODM / Sequelize ORM
                     ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
