> [!NOTE]
> **Why three tiers?** Separation of concerns → scalability → independent deployment. The frontend can be hosted on **Vercel/Netlify**, backend on **Render/Railway**, and database on **MongoDB Atlas** — this is the **cloud-native deployment** pattern KTU examiners love to see in viva.

